<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>Fm</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
.Fm                Bbm   Eb          Ab
 Qaygʻudamisan yigʻlama, muhtojmisan oʻylanma,
.Fm                 Bbm  Eb            F#
 Bedavomisan gʻashlanma, darding uchun yugurma.

[C1]
.     Fm     Eb        Bbm    Eb          Ab
   // Masih sen uchun kelgan, olam nurga toʻlgan,
.  Eb        Bbm     Eb           Ab
   Sen buni bilasan nimaga ishonmaysan? //
.      Fm     Bbm   Eb    Ab
   Sen buni bilasan nega kelmaysan?

[V2]
.Fm                 Bbm   Eb             Ab
 Darding uchun fol ochma, boyliging deb kekkayma,
.Fm               Bbm   Eb         Ab
 Baxtliman deb oʻtirma, bari buni befoyda.

[C2]
.  Fm    Eb         Bbm  Eb            Ab
   Masih sen uchun kelgan, olam nurga toʻlgan,
.      Fm     Bbm   Eb      Ab
   Sen buni bilasan nimaga ishonmaysan?
.  Eb               Bbm    Eb           Ab
   Yolgʻiz U yordam berar, Oʻz panohida asrar,
.  Eb  Fm       Bbm       Eb             Ab
   Sen bundan qochmagin, insonlardek yashagin.
.  Fm             Bbm     Eb             Ab
   Sen bundan qochmagin, hammalardek yashagin.</lyrics>
<title>Masih sen uchun kelgan</title>
</song>